    <releaseNotes>'Merged PR 10927: [PrimeScanSpofiTestMethod] Fix EngineeringSpofiOutputFolderPath filename with invalid syntax.'
'Merged PR 10896: fixing ScanSpofi cumulative Total Capture Count'
'Merged PR 10804: [PrimeScanHRYStfTestMethod] to improve UNTESTED-8 read out'
'Merged PR 10792: [PrimeScanLYATestMethod] Optimization for SPOFI to include partition name.'
'Merged PR 10518: SPOFI: adding new VectorCountOffset optional parameter'
'Merged PR 10391: [Scan][SpoFi] Adding disable options for pattern lookup and label reading'
'Merged PR 10348: [ScanLYATestMethod] Enable single-plist-only execution with SPOFI logging capability.'</releaseNotes>
